## Assets License (All Rights Reserved)

All visual, brand, and content assets in this repository are **proprietary** and may NOT be used, copied, modified, or distributed without explicit written permission from DominDev.

### Protected Assets Include

| Category | Location | Description |
|----------|----------|-------------|
| **Images** | `assets/images/` | All photographs, graphics, screenshots |
| **Brand Assets** | Various | Logos, favicons, OG images |
| **Typography** | `assets/fonts/` | Custom font configurations (note: fonts themselves have their own licenses) |
| **Written Content** | `*.html`, `data/` | Marketing copy, descriptions, chatbot responses |
| **Design System** | N/A | Visual design, color palette, layout compositions |

### Permitted Uses

- **Learning**: Study the code architecture and implementation techniques
- **Inspiration**: Use design concepts as reference for your own original work
- **Personal Projects**: Fork and modify for non-commercial personal use
- **Education**: Reference in tutorials, courses, or technical writing

### Prohibited Uses (Without Permission)

- Using DominDev brand assets, logos, or trademarks
- Copying the visual design 1:1 for commercial products
- Redistributing assets in templates, themes, or UI kits
- Claiming authorship or removing attribution
- Using images or graphics in any project without explicit permission

